WEBVTT

57:13.900 --> 57:14.859
Who are you guys?

57:16.025 --> 57:16.567
It was you?

57:16.567 --> 57:18.025
He murdered my younger sister!

57:18.192 --> 57:19.400
I must take revenge!

57:19.567 --> 57:21.067
We'll be in peace only
if we finish him off!

57:21.192 --> 57:22.734
We must kill him with our own hands!

57:22.984 --> 57:25.442
It's our duty to ensure that
he gets the right punishment.

57:25.984 --> 57:27.359
In the name of exacting revenge...

57:27.442 --> 57:29.317
don't ruin your lives.

57:29.650 --> 57:30.150
Now, leave!

57:30.609 --> 57:31.775
-Sir...
-I said, leave!
